thread.title: Lizbeth Clay
thread.title_full: Vital Choice reviewed by Lizbeth Clay

author: Lizbeth Clay
title: Lizbeth Clay
text: I am very excited to try this salmon oil and krill oil. The fact that the salmon oil is extracted from the salmon heads is awesome to me for two reasons. One is that the heads contain so much goodness and this goodness is often thrown away! Not so with Vital Choice. Good for me, and honoring of the fish. Both of these oils seem to be cultivated and extracted with awareness of sustainability and care for the ecosystem. I will be back!
